OL,6,FIn an update from , Superintendent
OL,7,FRoss Evans said: "Dyfed-Powys Police
OL,8,Fcontinue to investigate the serious
OL,9,Fincident that took place at Amman
OL,10,FValley School in Carmarthenshire this
OL,11,Fmorning.
OL,13,F"We received a call just after 11.20am
OL,14,Fadvising us people were injured
OL,15,Ffollowing an incident at the school.
OL,17,F"Emergency services immediately
OL,18,Fattended, and the school was locked
OL,19,Fdown for the safety of everyone on the
OL,20,Fpremises.
