OL,6,F"I am aware that there is footage of
OL,7,Fthe incident currently circulating on
OL,8,Fsocial media and would ask that this
OL,9,Fis removed to preserve the integrity
OL,10,Fof the ongoing investigation, and to
OL,11,Favoid further distress to those
OL,12,Finvolved.
OL,14,F"I would also ask that people do not
OL,15,Fspeculate while there is a police
OL,16,Finvestigation ongoing, and to refer to
OL,17,Fofficial channels for factual updates."
OL,19,FHe said there will be an increased
OL,20,Fpolice presence in the coming days as
OL,21,Fthe investigation continues.
